# Newton Public API

The free verification layer. `1 == 1`

## Endpoints

**POST /verify** - Verify text against constraints

**GET /health** - Status check

**GET /constraints** - List available constraints

## Deploy

Push to GitHub, connect to Render.com or Fly.io, deploy as Docker.

## Local

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python newton_public.py
```

